nflreadr update: thanks to @_pranavrajaram, new data dictionaries have been added for ESPN QBR, combine, injuries, depth charts, and trades data! You can check them out online in the "Dictionaries" section: https://t.co/E99DHmxVSU 

#rstats #nflverse https://t.co/Q2Zi3oBV7d

The Christmas holiday was a bit crazy this year and not only did I fail to post model outputs and game predictions, but I also messed up a bunch of fantasy lineups too :(.  Oh well.  Here are the latest #nfl model outputs - what stands out? #nflverse https://t.co/2zq0HRlbTr https://t.co/5COPjdJ6gg
And this week's game projections - my beloved @steelers are sending off any all-time great this Monday evening, and my system likes their chances.  #herewego #nflverse https://t.co/FKoD2q8aov
